%2Fapps%2F342310%2Fss_eedd086652ab447a6e416fab16a96f769bfc1c61.600x338.jpg%3Ft%3D1512377152&h=4b00eb5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/342310/ss_0864cb868c87f14223443f9cf9b5b150e29f57c0.600x338.jpg?t=1512377152\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.akamai.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F342310%2Fss_0864cb868c87f14223443f9cf9b5b150e29f57c0.600x338.jpg%3Ft%3D1512377152&h=6df0d82b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/342310/ss_30ee00698dea8b05963267d8b3d4813637a195fe.600x338.jpg?t=1512377152\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.akamai.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F342310%2Fss_30ee00698dea8b05963267d8b3d4813637a195fe.600x338.jpg%3Ft%3D1512377152&h=be38f0ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/342310/ss_2d0a2c71bd623b3d6d96fbd129a3a8ed2fbc1a36.600x338.jpg?t=1512377152\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.akamai.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F342310%2Fss_2d0a2c71bd623b3d6d96fbd129a3a8ed2fbc1a36.600x338.jpg%3Ft%3D1512377152&h=ed7db3e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/342310/ss_5bfcfa902423e66ea6b09c07ce0d490cae9781fc.600x338.jpg?t=1512377152\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.akamai.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F342310%2Fss_5bfcfa902423e66ea6b09c07ce0d490cae9781fc.600x338.jpg%3Ft%3D1512377152&h=b6fad416&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/342310/ss_8786b82e8ec790bec558192ca01751e8e8fe90bf.600x338.jpg?t=1512377152\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.akamai.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F342310%2Fss_8786b82e8ec790bec558192ca01751e8e8fe90bf.600x338.jpg%3Ft%3D1512377152&h=ddaeb755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/342310/ss_55f7f51a5f033c34e0027b2d1bad8519592d3997.600x338.jpg?t=1512377152\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.akamai.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F342310%2Fss_55f7f51a5f033c34e0027b2d1bad8519592d3997.600x338.jpg%3Ft%3D1512377152&h=b80888ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Play as police</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iegHZ_UWWsA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiegHZ_UWWsA&d=92pX4Sr7uSLFo4sFRTCm32i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=b3cbf8dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iegHZ_UWWsA</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Play as rioters</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=1398&amp;v=oGAGfCpHGno\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D1398%26v%3DoGAGfCpHGno&d=92pX4Sr7uSLFo4sFRTCm32i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=9cae5a0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=1398&amp;v=oGAGfCpHGno</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Play as the Police</span><br />\n<br />\nEmploy numerous crowd-control tactics, both passive and aggressive.<br />\nCommand Assault, Tactical, and Ballistic squads.<br />\nCall in police trucks, water cannon or even a tank!<br />\nChoose whether to use smoke grenades, rubber and plastic bullets or even live ammunition.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Play as the Rioters</span><br />\n<br />\nInstruct Rioters (armed and passive) and Journalists.<br />\nIncite rage and cause the masses to act aggressively or try to calm the situation with tactical crowd reformation and retreats.<br />\nAttack authority with Molotov cocktails, fireworks, paper-bombs, rocks, street furniture and the power of the media.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Multiple Modes</span><br />\n<br />\nSixteen campaign levels split over four scenarios; Keratea (Greece), NoTAV (Italy), Indignados (Spain) and Arab Spring (Egypt).<br />\nSee the story unfold from both sides - play all thirty-two levels as the Rioters or the Police.<br />\nSingle player mode - play against the computer AI.<br />\nVersus mode &ndash; play with or against a friend or AI on the same computer.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">系統需求</span><br />\n最低配備:<br />\n作業系統: Windows 7 or higher<br />\n處理器: 3GHz Processor or better<br />\n記憶體: 4 GB 記憶體<br />\n顯示卡: HD Graphics 4000 or better<br />\nDirectX: 版本：9.0c<br />\n儲存空間: 3 GB 可用空間<br />\n<br />\n建議配備:<br />\n作業系統: Windows 10<br />\n處理器: 3.4GHz Processor<br />\n記憶體: 4 GB 記憶體<br />\n顯示卡: 2GB Dedicated VRAM<br />\nDirectX: 版本：9.0c<br />\n儲存空間: 3 GB 可用空間<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/342310/RIOT__Civil_Unrest/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F342310%2FRIOT__Civil_Unrest%2F&d=92pX4Sr7uSLFo4sFRTCm32i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=d9452a2b\" target=\"_blank\">http://store.steampowered.com/app/342310/RIOT__Civil_Unrest/</a>"},{"pid":"56ea1f925fdde24ad3f245cd66387d04f87420a7","tid":489093,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:49:44.000Z","msg":"今天我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74177b68792b117f2915a08559f550441c27387c","tid":489093,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:52:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今天我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7208a411a931cbc0bee2be26a5094baa13948732","tid":489093,"uid":64966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6667c25bea1a735c7c7444255d5b838fd798363","tid":489093,"uid"